{"tid":730750,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學啲STEM老師真係好撚廢","createTime":"2018-07-05T15:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:57:38.000Z","uid":42764,"like":114,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"02c5550cc115a2796b54156d0a7283eea9c30be9","tid":730750,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"Programming唔識，整係識用App inventor<br />\nArduino又唔識，連用幾多voltage都唔知<br />\n唔好講Ai更加深既concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買完部3d printer唔識用，物理老師整係識計數，插塊電路板都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解中學會有啲咁既垃圾老師教學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db485587fe8b4c46965548bb5729f8ff3108bf2d","tid":730750,"uid":42764,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"同唔識電腦去教電腦一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03ac6a67880f7fb097ac9fe10820dfad8801b8f","tid":730750,"uid":11001,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"識得晒呢堆嘢嘅人會去教中學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442dac05bc51ef0db9f4e80a8a19256eef0e6288","tid":730750,"uid":25431,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"老實講 高中老師9成9都係教你去考試(有啲上堂廢噏嘅唔計)<br />\n呢啲stem <br />\n日常有應用嘅產品 例如無線叉電 phy堂有時間咪講吓<br />\nProgramming/robotics就初中/課外活動請啲TA返嚟教就算啦<br />\n<br />\n不過 我自己就覺得<br />\nStem應該係要推廣到背後「肯試」嘅精神俾學生<br />\n而唔係話教到啲咩知識俾佢哋<br />\n所有programming/robotics嗰啲應該都只係一個媒介<br />\n<br />\n所以 既然堂上無時間俾學生試<br />\n咁老師又有啲咩可以做<br />\n咪唯有交返比課外活動/改校本課程 推郁班hea hea吓嘅老師去做+ensure學生有足夠時間自己試 囉"},{"pid":"1e85466889702940c99f7cdcff7e27ab670780ec","tid":730750,"uid":42764,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"e03ac6a67880f7fb097ac9fe10820dfad8801b8f","tid":730750,"uid":11001,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05